{"id": "art-26", "label": "Art. 26", "title": "Art. 26: Disjungerea acţiunii civile", "slug": "art-26", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 26: Disjungerea ac&#355;iunii civile </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1087539377\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2766\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1087539377\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Instan&#355;a poate dispune disjungerea ac&#355;iunii\ncivile, când solu&#355;ionarea acesteia determin&#259; dep&#259;&#351;irea\ntermenului rezonabil de solu&#355;ionare a ac&#355;iunii penale.\nSolu&#355;ionarea ac&#355;iunii civile r&#259;mâne în competen&#355;a\ninstan&#355;ei penale.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(2)Disjungerea se dispune de\nc&#259;tre instan&#355;&#259; din oficiu ori la cererea procurorului sau a\np&#259;r&#355;ilor.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1451544256\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2765\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1451544256\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Probele administrate pân&#259; la disjungere vor fi\nfolosite la solu&#355;ionarea ac&#355;iunii civile disjunse.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(4)[textul din Art. 26, alin. (4)\ndin partea 1, titlul II, capitolul II a fost abrogat la 01-feb-2014 de </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>Art. 102, punctul 16. din titlul III din Legea 255/2013</span><span\nstyle='color:black'>]</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(5)Încheierea prin care se disjunge\nac&#355;iunea civil&#259; este definitiv&#259;.</span></p>"}